          <l corresp="47"> by the good girl with choice jewels [Maṇimēkalai] there in the interior
            of that island;</l>
          <l corresp="50"> and (9) the realisation of the nature of all her previous
            births</l>
          <l corresp="49"> by her who had suffered through the unique pedestal of shining gems
            there;</l>
